---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const productData = {
  name: "Digital Couponing Guide",
  description: "Comprehensive guide to digital couponing, rewards programs, and smart shopping strategies to help you save money on everyday purchases."
};
---

<Layout 
  title="Digital Couponing Guide" 
  description={productData.description}
  product={productData}
>
  <!-- Featured Image Section -->
  <div class="relative h-[300px] sm:h-[400px] overflow-hidden">
    <img 
      src="/images/coupons/digital-couponing-hero.webp" 
      alt="Digital Couponing and Mobile Savings"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/50 to-black/20 flex items-center justify-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white text-center max-w-4xl px-4">
        Master the Art of Digital Couponing
      </h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">What is Digital Couponing?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Digital couponing is the modern way to save money using electronic or mobile coupons instead of traditional paper ones.
        These coupons can be found on retailer websites, apps, and dedicated coupon platforms.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Advantages of Digital Coupons:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>No printing or clipping required</li>
          <li>Easy to organize and track</li>
          <li>Often exclusive digital-only deals</li>
          <li>Instant savings at checkout</li>
          <li>Environmental friendly</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Where to Find Digital Coupons</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border-b pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Retailer Apps and Websites</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Most major retailers offer digital coupons through their mobile apps and websites.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Store loyalty program apps</li>
            <li>Retailer websites</li>
            <li>Email newsletters</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Coupon Websites and Apps</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Dedicated coupon platforms aggregate deals from multiple retailers.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Rakuten</li>
            <li>Ibotta</li>
            <li>Coupons.com</li>
            <li>RetailMeNot</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="border-b pb-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Browser Extensions</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            These tools automatically find and apply coupon codes when shopping online.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Honey</li>
            <li>Capital One Shopping</li>
            <li>Rakuten Extension</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Digital Couponing Best Practices</h2>
      
      <div class="bg-primary/5 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-4">
          <li>
            <strong>Create a Digital System:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Organize your digital coupons by category and expiration date.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Stack Digital Savings:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Combine store apps, cashback apps, and browser extensions for maximum savings.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Check Before Shopping:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Always look for digital coupons before making a purchase, both online and in-store.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Enable Notifications:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Stay updated on new deals and expiring coupons through app notifications.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Compare Prices:</strong>
            <p class="mt-2">Use price comparison tools alongside digital coupons to ensure the best deal.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Common Digital Couponing Mistakes</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-8">
        <li>Forgetting to activate offers before shopping</li>
        <li>Not reading the terms and conditions</li>
        <li>Missing out on stackable savings opportunities</li>
        <li>Letting digital coupons expire</li>
        <li>Not checking for better deals on other platforms</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Getting Started with Digital Couponing</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Begin by downloading your favorite stores' apps and signing up for their loyalty programs.
          Install 1-2 reliable browser extensions and familiarize yourself with major cashback platforms.
        </p>
        <p>
          Remember to check our other guides and resources for more advanced saving strategies and tips
          on combining digital coupons with other money-saving techniques.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
